Package: kodamaR
Title: R Wrapper for the Kodama-Cpp Library
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Stefano", "Cacciatore", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "tkcaccia@gmail.com")
  )
Author: Stefano Cacciatore [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Stefano Cacciatore <tkcaccia@gmail.com>
Description: Thin R bindings for the standalone kodama-cpp C++ library.
    The package exposes KODAMA matrix optimization with KNN and PLS-LDA
    classifiers on CPU, NVIDIA CUDA, and Apple Metal while keeping all
    numerical kernels in kodama-cpp.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports:
    Rcpp
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: kodama-cpp; optional CUDA Toolkit or Apple Metal frameworks
URL: https://github.com/tkcaccia/kodama-r
BugReports: https://github.com/tkcaccia/kodama-r/issues
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
